flowchart TD
  %% Agentic Delivery Framework — Overview Flow (GitHub profile)
  DL[Delivery Lead<br/>(outside Codespaces)] --> B{Select Sprint<br/>via Projects Iterations}
  B -->|For each Story| C{Codespace exists?}
  C -->|No| D[Create Codespace<br/>(prebuilds, secrets, retention)]
  C -->|Yes| E[Resume Codespace]
  D --> DEV[Start Developers inside Codespace<br/>(Aider/Cline/Continue/OpenHands)]
  E --> DEV
  DEV --> G[Create branch<br/>feat/&lt;issue-key&gt;]
  G --> H[Implement slices<br/>plan → edit → run → test]
  H --> I[Open PR with checklist<br/>"Closes #&lt;issue-id&gt;" + Story Preview]
  I --> J{{PR / CR Gates}}
  J --> J1[CI / Tests]
  J --> J2[QA Verification]
  J --> J3[Security Review<br/>(CodeQL / deps)]
  J --> J4[Automated Review]
  J --> J5[Human Reviewer(s)]
  J --> J6[Performance Budget Checks]
  J -->|All pass| K[Merge → Close Issue →<br/>Update Sprint board]
  J -->|Fail| DEV
  K --> L{More Stories in Sprint?}
  L -->|Yes| B
  L -->|No| M[Stop/Hibernate Codespace<br/>Generate Metrics + Pulse Increment]
  M --> N[Sprint Review & Retro<br/>Delivery Lead plans next Sprint]
